Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: As Kamala Harris gives her convention speech tonight, she will not mention the victims. She will not say their names or express remorse to their families. Kamala says she wants to talk about the FUTURE—but she has stolen the future of Laken Riley, Rachel Morin, and precious Jocelyn.
